managePositionBatch.t.sol
├── when call is reentrant
│  └── it should revert
└── when call is not reentrant
   ├── when caller is not a registered operator
   │  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
   └── when caller is a registered operator
      ├── when management and accounting instruction list lengths are mismatched
      │  └── it should revert with MismatchedLengths
      └── when management and accounting instruction list lengths are matched
         └── it should execute the provided pairs of management and optional accounting instructions sequentially, and return the resulting position values and value changes when applicable.
